- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is a possible category as the paper introduces differential forms for differential dynamic logic, which may involve mathematical software. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implementation of the proof calculus and may involve software engineering techniques.
